headline: California could get its first gasoline pipeline. Would that lower gas prices?
summary: The proposed Western Gateway Pipeline from Phillips 66 and Kinder Morgan would deliver gasoline, diesel and jet fuel to Arizona and California from as fast east as Missouri by 2029.
